            <lg xml:id="TK1287">
<l>uytta laṟintu puṉalpāy pavarēpōṟ </l>
<l>poytta laṟinteṉ pulantu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like those who leap into a stream which they know will carry them off, why should a wife feign dislike which she knows cannot hold out long?</l>
